# skill: qa

## Purpose
Run after every code block before committing. Prevents regressions.

## Checklist
- [ ] TypeScript: no `any`, explicit return types on all functions
- [ ] No `framer-motion` imports (use `motion/react`)
- [ ] Tailwind: no hardcoded colors outside CSS variables
- [ ] Supabase: any new column → `database.types.ts` regenerated
- [ ] WhatsApp number: ONLY via `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_WHATSAPP_NUMBER` (never hardcoded)
- [ ] No `console.log` left in production code
- [ ] No DB column renames without a SQL migration first
- [ ] App Router only — no `getServerSideProps`, no `pages/` directory usage
- [ ] Server Components by default — `'use client'` only when strictly necessary
- [ ] After migration: run `supabase gen types typescript` and update `types/database.types.ts`
